    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously preserved to look and drive like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no dents, scratches, or chips to be found. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with leather that remains supple and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and serviced regularly. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that requires nothing but a new home.",
