    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, making it a reliable choice for any driver. While the exterior and interior show minor signs of normal wear and tear consistent with its age, the car remains very clean and presentable. Buyers can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready for the road with no immediate major repairs needed.",
